ai-kv22.4:1.1_0: There are things that are maturity because of conception.
ai-kv22.4:1.3_0: There is in the womb in a teaching Dhamma that is pregnant, moderation, observed by the subtle, comprehension of precepts and observances, and the rest of the sense faculties.
ai-kv22.4:1.4_0: And you don’t keep on doing it.
ai-kv22.4:1.5_0: There is no way to teach the Dhamma in the pregnanting of the Teaching, the Monastic Law, and the worst in the past.
ai-kv22.4:1.7_0: There is no way to teach the Dhamma.
ai-kv22.4:1.7_1: ‘In the past, future, or present, and internally, you should say.
ai-kv22.4:2.1_0: There are things that are maturity because of conception.
ai-kv22.4:2.3_0: Have two conditions for the arising of right view:
ai-kv22.4:2.4_0: the words of another and proper attention.
ai-kv22.4:2.6_0: And there are two conditions for the arising of right view:
ai-kv22.4:3.1_0: There are things that are maturity because of conception.
ai-kv22.4:3.4_0: And you don’t keep on doing it.
